<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id1284ad1a-f87d-11ef-b94d-97e317d2120c" identifier="/us/usc/t4/s2"><num value="2">§ 2.</num><heading> Same; additional stars</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">On the admission of a new State into the Union one star shall be added to the union of the flag; and such addition shall take effect on the fourth day of July then next succeeding such admission.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id1284ad1b-f87d-11ef-b94d-97e317d2120c">(<ref href="/us/act/1947-07-30/ch389">July 30, 1947, ch. 389</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/61/642">61 Stat. 642</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
